The paper focuses on image synthesis using conditional GANs, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed model also involves an advanced auxiliary classifier, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the convergence speed of the model, which is related to optimization and algorithms (cs.GR). Finally, the experimental results involve image quality evaluation, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
